<h1><i class="fa fa-search"></i>Searching for Files</h1>

<ol class="breadcrumb">
	<li><a href="#help"><i class="fa fa-question-circle"></i>Help</a></li>
	<li><a href="#help/working-with-files"><i class="fa fa-file"></i>Working with Files</a></li>
	<li><i class="fa fa-search"></i>Searching for Files</li>
</ol>

<div class="content">
	<p><%= application.name %> offers a number of ways to search your files. </p>

	<ol>
		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-eye"></i>The Search Menu</h2>
			<p>To view the available options for viewing files and folders, mouse over the Search menu on your <a href="#help/getting-started/using-desktop">Desktop</a> or in a <a href="#apps/file-browser">File Browser</a> window. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<img class="dropdown menu" src="images/help/working-with-files/searching-for-files/search-menu@2x.png" />
				<div class="caption">The Search Menu</div>
			</div>
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-font"></i>Search by Name</h2>
			<p>The most common way to search is to search files or directories by their file or folder name. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<img class="search" src="images/help/working-with-files/searching-for-files/search-by-name@2x.png" />
				<div class="caption">Search by Name</div>
			</div>
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-file"></i>Search by Kind</h2>
			<p>Another way to search files is to search by file kind. To search by file kind, type in the file extension (txt, jpg, etc.) of kind of file that you are looking for. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<img class="search" src="images/help/working-with-files/searching-for-files/search-by-kind@2x.png" />
				<div class="caption">Search by Kind</div>
			</div>
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-download"></i>Search by Size</h2>
			<p>You can search files by size, specifying whether you are looking for files that are larger than, equal to, or less than a particular file size. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<img class="search" src="images/help/working-with-files/searching-for-files/search-by-size@2x.png" />
				<div class="caption">Search by Size</div>
			</div>
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-calendar-alt"></i>Search by Date</h2>
			<p>You can search files by create date, update date, or access date, specifying whether you are looking for files that are before, on, or after that date. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<img class="search" src="images/help/working-with-files/searching-for-files/search-by-create-date@2x.png" />
				<div class="caption">Search by Create Date</div>
			</div>
			<div class="figure">
				<img class="search" src="images/help/working-with-files/searching-for-files/search-by-modify-date@2x.png" />
				<div class="caption">Search by Modify Date</div>
			</div>
			<div class="figure">
				<img class="search" src="images/help/working-with-files/searching-for-files/search-by-access-date@2x.png" />
				<div class="caption">Search by Access Date</div>
			</div>
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-calendar-alt"></i>Search by Sharing</h2>
			<p>You can search files by its sharing status. You can search for files shared with you by a particular connection, search for files shared by you, and search for files or directories that have links associated with them. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<img class="search" src="images/help/working-with-files/searching-for-files/search-by-shared-with-me@2x.png" />
				<div class="caption">Search by Shared with Me</div>
			</div>
			<div class="figure">
				<img class="search" src="images/help/working-with-files/searching-for-files/search-by-shared-by-me@2x.png" />
				<div class="caption">Search by Shared by Me</div>
			</div>
			<div class="figure">
				<img class="search" src="images/help/working-with-files/searching-for-files/search-by-links@2x.png" />
				<div class="caption">Search by Links</div>
			</div>
		</li>
	</ol>
</div>